// E2E Tests for {{ entityName }}
// Base URL: {{ baseUrl }}
// API Path: {{ apiPath }}

// Test sequence:
// 1. Health check - verify API is running
// 2. CREATE - POST to create entity, capture ID
// 3. READ LIST - GET all entities, verify created one exists
// 4. READ ONE - GET by ID, verify data
// 5. UPDATE - PUT to modify entity
// 6. DELETE - DELETE entity
// 7. VERIFY DELETE - GET should return 404

// Test body should include common fields:
// - name/title (string)
// - description (string, optional)
// - Any required fields from entity schema
